    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dukkido is a physics-based, Co-Op Action RTS where you directly control your Captain and a squad of minions. Collect resources, uncover artifacts, solve puzzles, and build your army while unraveling the secrets of the Relic Frontier. Play solo or with up to 5 players in chaotic Online Co-Op, and complete over 5 unique objectives in Dukkido's fully handcrafted mission-based adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186280/extras/0d1f1f3a9a89e8c7bad274fa023bc738.poster.avif?t=1767626793\" width=800 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186280/extras/0d1f1f3a9a89e8c7bad274fa023bc738.webm?t=1767626793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186280/extras/0d1f1f3a9a89e8c7bad274fa023bc738.mp4?t=1767626793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every mission features a familiar level, but with countless different layouts, puzzles, enemies, and secrets to uncover. You can choose to follow the mission objective and collect resources, or you can instead delve into one of Dukkido's many mysteries. Beware the looming crackdown timer, where the planet itself will grow increasingly hostile until you can safely extract with your army.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dukkido is home to dozens of unique enemies, each featuring unique combat mechanics to test you and your dogs of war.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186280/extras/8fd4e8a933d458d4ce185d2c8c0236cc.poster.avif?t=1767626793\" width=800 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186280/extras/8fd4e8a933d458d4ce185d2c8c0236cc.webm?t=1767626793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186280/extras/8fd4e8a933d458d4ce185d2c8c0236cc.mp4?t=1767626793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the Project</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dukkido is being developed by MariSuCho, a small independent team of three developers on a shoestring budget. We're doing our best to turn Dukkido into something everyone can enjoy, without compromising what we believe makes games fun and enchanting. Dukkido is still in its early stages, and every little bit of support helps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We're aiming for a demo release very soon. If you want to follow the project, please check out our Discord for the most frequent updates, and to participate in our growing community! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186280/extras/a59d0e348bb80c56311b6a8d4ece0c60.poster.avif?t=1767626793\" width=800 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186280/extras/a59d0e348bb80c56311b6a8d4ece0c60.webm?t=1767626793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186280/extras/a59d0e348bb80c56311b6a8d4ece0c60.mp4?t=1767626793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
